description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Gatinho purrs with a rating of 75, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 150, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, Nine Lives for East, Box for South, and 8 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50752-29482-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [150 Votes, Top 9% Rating]
